establishment.address: 12, Super Yarn Market, Near Hajuri Chambers, Salabatpura, Surat

items.name: Chicken Manchurian
items.description: Delicious fried chicken in slightly sweet, hot & sour manchurian sauce. Chicken manchurian is an Indo Chinese food that is much popular in the Indian subcontinent.

items.name: Dragon Chicken
items.description: Dragon chicken made restaurant style in which chicken is fried till crispy and tossed in spicy sauce with dry red chilly.

items.name: Chicken Drums Of Heaven [Full]
items.description: A slight twist to your ordinary chicken lollipop, this chicken wings fried and tossed in schezwan sauce is a famous appetizer. The sauce make the chicken more succulent.

items.name: Chicken Singapuri Rice
items.description: Singapore fried rice is a Chinese fried rice variation made with rice, vegetables, soya sauce, curry powder, spices like ginger, garlic and chilli.

items.name: Chicken Singapuri Triple Rice With Gravy
items.description: Chicken Singapuri triple fried rice is a favourite Mumbai's street stalls sought after dish. The bright yellow colored rice and noodles, topped with fried noodles and yellowish chicken gravy are something that one cannot resist to taste.

items.name: Chicken Hakka Noodles
items.description: Chicken hakka noodles is a Chinese dish of cooked noodles tossed with boiled and shredded chicken and vegetables in Chinese sauces.

items.name: Foodies Junction Special Naan Chaap
items.description: The mutton naan chaap which is the naan sandwich which is made over maida bread cut into two and a mixture of mutton roasted all over the tawa is filled in the centre.

items.name: Chicken Bombay Bhel [Full]
items.description: Bombay bhel is a classic Bombay street side snack. It is made with puffed rice, tangy, sweet and spicy bhel chutney and fresh veggies.

items.name: Non Veg Hot And Sour Soup
Non Veg Manchow Soup
items.description: Chicken manchow is a dark brown Chinese soup. Chicken, carrots and other veggies simmered in mild flavors.
